# Security Problems

Classic Modbus has NO security:

* No encryption
* No authentication
* No integrity protection

Anyone on the network may:

* Read registers
* Write values
* Stop motors
* Change settings

This is a major issue in modern ICS security.

---

# Modern Security Approaches

Solutions:

* VPNs
* Firewalls
* Network segmentation
* Secure gateways
* TLS wrappers
* Industrial DMZs

There is also:

* Modbus Security (TLS-based)

But adoption is limited.

