# Example Complete Transaction

## Read Temperature

Client sends:

```text
Device 5
Read Holding Registers
Address 10
Count 1
```

Server responds:

```text
Register 10 = 253
```

Interpretation:

```text
25.3°C
```

(scale factor = 0.1)

---

# Modbus Data Scaling

Very common.

Raw register:

```text
253
```

Engineering value:

```text
25.3°C
```

Formula:

```text
Actual = Raw × Scale
```

